    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the group of studies or branches of knowledge concerned with facts and phenomena of the observable or quantifiable world, systematically arranged and showing the operation of general laws.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
